🏕Live Coding takes place every Wednesday and Thursday, from 14:30 UTC.

From the beginning, our educational work has been defined by 4 stages:

🚣‍♀️ learn-by-doing,   
👩‍🏭 collaborate,   
🏗 contribute,  
🙋‍♀️ make decisions.

Around this methodology, very interesting things emerge, new💡ideas take shape. [Andamio platform](https://www.andamio.io/) is an example of this: <https://www.andamio.io/>

![](https://ucarecdn.com/349f4f28-4cf6-4ccc-9380-3514d50691c3/-/preview/-/format/auto/-/quality/smart/)

![](https://ucarecdn.com/349f4f28-4cf6-4ccc-9380-3514d50691c3/-/preview/-/format/auto/-/quality/smart/)

Bring your ideas to the 🏕 Live coding. Zoom link in our calendar: <https://gimbalabs.com/calendar>
